scenes.description: The members of Justice banter before Elizabeth starts her turn at the typing game.
Elizabeth Rose Bloodflame takes her turn answering trivia questions on the giant keyboard.
Elizabeth finishes her turn and discusses her score with the group.
Raora Mocchiato takes her turn at the typing game.
Raora finishes her turn, and the group celebrates while Gigi prepares for her turn.
Gigi Murin begins her turn at the typing game.
